{"tid":185463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】滿客渡輪直撼愉景灣碼頭 窗框變形玻璃粉碎","createTime":"2017-04-03T13:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T13:14:42.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"992eb07e7c04359ddae71944769327f74a620875","tid":185463,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T13:04:01.000Z","msg":"愉景灣碼頭發生撞船事故！晚上近8時半，一艘駛往愉景灣的渡輪在準備泊埋碼頭時，疑失控直撞碼頭。據現場讀者拍下的現場情況，見碼頭一組窗框被撞至嚴重變形，玻璃窗粉碎，散滿地上。現場消息稱，船上乘客幾乎爆滿，在撞船事故中，至少一名女子頸部受傷需要送院治理。"},{"pid":"84fdd458d65578851fac1cd0a0f5bd4b5b914b3c","tid":185463,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T13:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170403/large/1491224074_1d00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170403%2Flarge%2F1491224074_1d00.jpg&h=00de85fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170403/56518736\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170403%2F56518736&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=8800e640\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170403%2F56518736&h=c1c4501c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170403/56518736</a>"},{"pid":"4e91d0e6e2e4e3ad3b2539d7e03286e3fbdf58ed","tid":185463,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T13:10:16.000Z","msg":"我又唔信傷一件咁少"},{"pid":"746bc90c08c622b2384410fc1a33dec5aabde12c","tid":185463,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T13:14:42.000Z","msg":"世越號事件=林鄭2.0"}]}